Date: 1995-04-02

Title: Loop scattering in two-dimensional QCD

Authors: E. Abdalla, M.C.B. Abdalla

Comments: 6 pages, plain tex.

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D52 (1995) 6660-6663

Using the integrability conditions that we recently obtained in QCD$_2$ withmassless fermions, we arrive at a sufficient number of conservation laws to beable to fix the scattering amplitudes involving a local version of the Wilsonloop operator.